{"type":"message","id":"64dad3d3","parentId":"374dccc1","timestamp":"2026-04-17T03:45:42.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Beleza. Abre o VS Code:\n\n```bash\ncode ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n```\n\nProcura essa parte no arquivo:\n\n```json\n\"channels\": {\n  \"whatsapp\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"allowFrom\": [\n      \"+5567996583158\"\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\nE muda pra:\n\n```json\n\"channels\": {\n  \"whatsapp\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"allowFrom\": [\n      \"+5567996583158\"\n    ],\n    \"autoReply\": true,\n    \"triggerWords\": [\"oi\", \"olá\", \"bom dia\", \"boa tarde\", \"boa noite\", \"voz\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\nSalva (Ctrl+S) e depois roda:\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\nMe avisa quando terminar."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"qwen3.5:cloud","usage":{"input":38959,"output":217,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39176,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1776397542332}}
